&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Microblink uses cutting-edge technology to create an environment where top talented industry experts have an opportunity to grow and lead innovation. We are looking for like-minded individuals to join us in our quest to bridge the gap between companies and customers, citizens and governments, humans, and AI.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are constantly growing and investing in new talent in different areas and for different experience levels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We like to expand our team with people who excel in their student, private, or professional projects, but we are not exclusive about criteria - the best results are accomplished by combining different experiences, ideas, and viewpoints.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Send us your CV if you think we sparked your interest. Feel free to add a link to some of your projects or ideas!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We wish you the best of luck!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Microblink Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Microblink LLC is an equal opportunity employer committed to diversity and inclusion in the workplace. This policy applies to all employment practices within our organization, from hiring to the end of your business relationship with us. Accordingly, this job advertisement is equally applicable to all people and Microblink will make a hiring decision based solely on qualifications, merit, and business needs. We prohibit discrimination of any kind based on race, color, sex, religion, sexual orientation, national origin, disability, genetic information, pregnancy, or any other protected characteristic as outlined by federal, state, or local laws, as well as our internal policies and culture.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For detailed information on how we process personal data, please read our Privacy Policy&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://microblink.com/privacy-policy/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://microblink.com/privacy-policy/&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;https://microblink.com/privacy-policy/&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;or reach out to our Data Protection Officer at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;mailto:privacy@microblink.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;mailto:privacy@microblink.com&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;privacy@microblink.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are reviewing applications from candidates based in Croatia ideally. Candidates must have residency and work authorization. We do not offer visa sponsorship or B2B engagement at the moment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Microblink is an Identity Intelligence company helping organizations establish trust across digital journeys. By combining identity documents, biometrics, and payment card verification into a single platform, Microblink enables continuous identity control. Its technology is used globally to combat fraud, improve decision-making, and create secure user experiences across onboarding, authentication, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, Microblink&#39;s solutions operate in more than 195 countries and territories, processing billions of identity transactions annually. Through advanced testing and fraud detection capabilities, including its proprietary Fraud Lab, the company continuously improves the accuracy and reliability of its identity verification technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested in learning more?&lt;a href=&quot;https://microblink.com/demo/&quot;&gt; Explore our tech in action&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;mid-level&amp;nbsp; Quality Assurance&amp;nbsp; Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;to join the team responsible for our &lt;strong&gt;identity document scanning and verification SDK.&lt;/strong&gt; The SDK powers identity verification experiences &lt;strong&gt;across Android, iOS, and Web applications, including cross-platform frameworks &lt;/strong&gt;(e.g.&amp;nbsp; React Native and Flutter). It is available as both cloud and self-hosted solutions and is used by customers worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll work alongside experienced QA engineers that continuously help ensure the SDK performs reliably across different platforms, devices, and real-world conditions. You&#39;ll validate new features, discover and investigate edge cases, and verify that each release delivers a consistent experience across environments. Given the variety of the long tail of exceptions rooted in the global business of Microblink, testing will require a good amount of creativity and savvy usage of the modern AI tools, and an acquired taste for automation and scalability of testing processes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your impact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll spend most of your time validating SDK integrations across Android, iOS and Web platforms using internally developed test applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rather than testing a single application, you&#39;ll be validating how our SDK behaves when integrated into applications across different platforms, devices and operating systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your day-to-day work will include exploring scenarios such as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Various types of identity documents, including passports, ID cards and driver&#39;s licenses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Different devices and operating system versions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Desktop and mobile browsers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Varying lighting conditions and camera quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SDK behaviour across Android, iOS, Web and cross-platform integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Edge cases that could impact user experience or document recognition quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
